<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA55">
<l>eṉṟu maṟantaṟiyē ṉēḻpiṟappu meppoḻutu</l>
<l>niṉṟu niṉaippoḻiyā nīrmaiyāl – veṉṟi</l>
<l>yaṭalāḻi koṇṭa vaṟivaṉē yiṉpak</l>
<l>kaṭalāḻi nīyaruḷik kāṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I never forget, because of [my] nature</l>
<l>that never stops thinking constantly of the seven births.</l>
<l>O knowing one with the victorious, murderous discus,</l>
<l>You of the ocean  of bliss, look [at me] graciously.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
